(firstQuint)Evaluate Safety and Pharmacokinetics of Minocin (Minocycline) for Injection in Subjects With Renal Insufficiency.

 The purpose of this study is to collect safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics (PK) data on a single dose of Minocin(R) (minocycline) for Injection in subjects with renal insufficiency and in subjects receiving hemodialysis therapy.

 The safety, tolerability, and PK data will support the compound as a potential clinical candidate in Europe and will inform the development of future Phase 2/3 studies.

